  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After humanity's catastrophic mistakes, the gates to the afterlife have been opened, and darkness has consumed our world. You are the last survivor, brave enough to take on the unholy forces that have seized the continent. Your mission is to fight, survive, and restore order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/1c71339bb0e39c825efb3f11dd11d9ce.poster.avif?t=1738292443\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/1c71339bb0e39c825efb3f11dd11d9ce.webm?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat:</strong> Slay hordes of monsters and face off against powerful bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Progression:</strong> Earn experience and currency during each expedition, unlock new gear, and upgrade your shelter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Atmosphere:</strong> Explore a procedurally generated dark world filled with dangers and secrets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.poster.avif?t=1738292443\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.webm?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.mp4?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breathe life into this desolate land and prove that even in the deepest abyss, hope still endures!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After humanity's catastrophic mistakes, the gates to the afterlife have been opened, and darkness has consumed our world. You are the last survivor, brave enough to take on the unholy forces that have seized the continent. Your mission is to fight, survive, and restore order.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/1c71339bb0e39c825efb3f11dd11d9ce.poster.avif?t=1738292443\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/1c71339bb0e39c825efb3f11dd11d9ce.webm?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Combat:</strong> Slay hordes of monsters and face off against powerful bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Progression:</strong> Earn experience and currency during each expedition, unlock new gear, and upgrade your shelter.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Atmosphere:</strong> Explore a procedurally generated dark world filled with dangers and secrets.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.poster.avif?t=1738292443\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.webm?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1670530/extras/93c96c24dfd8c087b7eed58b5dd02c3f.mp4?t=1738292443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Breathe life into this desolate land and prove that even in the deepest abyss, hope still endures!</p>",
